Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.70,0:00:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿幾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.01,0:00:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算做什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.33,0:00:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們好心陪這只狗玩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.76,0:00:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麽意見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.41,0:00:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.99,0:00:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是一副囂張的態度嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.20,0:00:24.72,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(860,650)\c&H1414FF&}せき
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.20,0:00:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過啊 你已經不再是{\c&H1414FF&}隻{\r}了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.42,0:00:32.00,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1080,650)\c&H1414FF&}クラミツハ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.42,0:00:32.00,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1240,650)\c&H1414FF&}せき
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.42,0:00:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來只有擁有枸雅家正統血脈的我才配成為{\c&H1414FF&}暗密刀{\r}的{\c&H1414FF&}隻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋 瞧不起我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.86,0:00:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我住手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.35,0:00:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在做什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.42,0:00:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麽多人欺負一個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.89,0:00:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.76,0:00:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是生面孔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.58,0:00:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.50,0:00:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.76,0:00:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰說你可以走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.30,0:00:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 都說了叫你站住!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.27,0:01:10.79,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(620,650)\c&H1414FF&}クラミツハ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.27,0:01:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了沒 {\c&H1414FF&}暗密刀{\r}是屬於我的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.18,0:01:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你靠這家夥來當盾牌 已經是過去式了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.01,0:01:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可悲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.98,0:01:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真叫人看不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.09,0:01:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過只是向前飛幾步就晃成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.90,0:01:30.59,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(670,650)\c&H1414FF&}せき
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.90,0:01:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的有當{\c&H1414FF&}隻{\r}的資格嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.27,0:01:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看你是活得不耐煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.42,0:01:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篤史大人 夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.69,0:01:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 做得太過火了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.11,0:01:41.06,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,650)\c&H1414FF&}ククリ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.11,0:01:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1414FF&}玖吼理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.09,0:01:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別妨礙我 匡平
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.77,0:01:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手啊 篤史
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.64,0:01:50.80,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(720,650)\c&H1414FF&}せき
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.64,0:01:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是{\c&H1414FF&}隻{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.81,0:01:52.96,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(850,650)\c&H1414FF&}カカシ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.81,0:01:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能在光天化日之下用{\c&H1414FF&}案山子{\r}來傷人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.60,0:01:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算你走運 阿幾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.27,0:02:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.52,0:02:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.54,0:02:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然有所耳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.42,0:02:11.08,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(695,650)\c&H1414FF&}カカシ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.42,0:02:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是{\c&H1414FF&}案山子{\r}嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是村子外面來的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.14,0:02:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.05,0:02:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麽會來這裡...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.10,0:02:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你 給我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.98,0:02:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你救了這隻狗對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就應該一直照顧它到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.44,0:02:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真囂張
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.24,0:02:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.16,0:02:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這便是我們與瀨能千波野老師的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,

