Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.25,0:02:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫瀨能千波野
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.62,0:02:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將代替生病的谷崎老師
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.82,0:02:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天起我就是各位的老師了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.18,0:02:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.24,0:02:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上我認為她是一名好老師
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.63,0:03:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那學期 學校裡顯得很開朗並且充滿了活力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追憶的肖像
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.15,0:03:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匡平大人你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.47,0:03:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.77,0:03:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫我大人 總感覺是在挖苦我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.20,0:03:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麽關系 我說的是實話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.83,0:03:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和那個老師怎麽樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.41,0:03:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得瀨能老師很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.73,0:03:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是喜歡她才這麽說的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.25,0:03:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿幾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.56,0:03:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是那時候的狗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.48,0:03:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女人硬推給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.07,0:03:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被老師?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.67,0:03:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒想到你居然會答應呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.03,0:03:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被她硬逼的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.59,0:03:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個厚臉皮的女人 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.95,0:03:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常的你肯定會大發脾氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 說得對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.59,0:04:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別來問我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.15,0:04:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跑 聽話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.46,0:04:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿幾什麽時候人變得這麽好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他平時就是那樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.20,0:04:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 他看起來就像是普通的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師再見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.23,0:04:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.89,0:04:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.14,0:04:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麽事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.85,0:04:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細一看還真是個美人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你也應該清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡對於年輕人來說缺少刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長話短說 你和我交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.78,0:04:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別這樣捉弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.30,0:04:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你放開
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.99,0:04:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可真兇悍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:05:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加激起我的鬥志了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.38,0:05:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖地按照我說的去做 不會讓你吃虧的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.77,0:05:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.28,0:05:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真傷腦筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.49,0:05:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你和枸雅家的兒子起了爭執
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是對方先...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.39,0:05:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你對他動手了 這是事實吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.54,0:05:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.70,0:05:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這村子裡掌管神社的枸雅家和日向家的一切都是絕對的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.93,0:05:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你還想繼續在這裡工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請牢記這點並且注意不再有任何輕率的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:06:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們開始上課
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師沒有任何錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.06,0:06:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯的人難道不是篤史嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.90,0:06:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麽只責備老師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對我抱怨也無濟於事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你直接去找校長說不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.50,0:06:20.95,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(740,650)\c&H1414FF&}せき
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.50,0:06:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你是{\c&H1414FF&}隻{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.35,0:06:27.96,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(500,650)\c&H1414FF&}せき
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.35,0:06:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是規定了就算是{\c&H1414FF&}隻{\r} 在學校裡還是得聽老師的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就去對他本人說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你辦不到的話 就閉上嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩緒 走廊打掃好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.30,0:06:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匡平?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.33,0:06:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匡平 要吃晚飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.69,0:06:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪兒 匡平
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽了 匡平君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我會保護老師的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.66,0:07:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.29,0:07:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果校長或是篤史對你做了什麽 一定要和我說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:20.37,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(400,650)\c&H1414FF&}せき
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是{\c&H1414FF&}隻{\r} 是這座村子裡特別的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.59,0:07:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可靠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.66,0:07:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但老師不是很喜歡你這種仰仗自己有特權的態度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心 老師可是大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.17,0:07:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會自己照顧自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你為我擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.96,0:07:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天平屋和森田請假嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 我媽媽叫我不要跟老師走得太近
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.13,0:08:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師你做了什麽壞事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.24,0:08:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這種事 我想是你媽媽誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我們開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.26,0:08:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.80,0:08:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經散完步了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.55,0:08:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿幾是魔性的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.71,0:08:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候他殘殺了無數的小動物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.22,0:08:40.70,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(580,650)\c&H1414FF&}せき
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.22,0:08:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果繼續讓他當{\c&H1414FF&}隻{\r} 總有一天會鬧出人命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.97,0:08:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿幾君 你不來上學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.16,0:08:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意去讓別人討厭我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.15,0:09:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的人只會冷淡地對待遭受到排擠的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.55,0:09:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一個人不感到寂寞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.93,0:09:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就是一個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.20,0:09:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡真是個腐朽不堪的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.03,0:09:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}瀨能和學生的父親搞外遇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.77,0:09:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.39,0:09:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.59,0:09:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種胡扯的東西 是哪個傢夥寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.46,0:09:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你冷靜下 這些孩子怎麽會做這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.31,0:09:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師怎麽自己翹課出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.61,0:10:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.68,0:10:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什麽...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.82,0:10:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 沒什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.42,0:10:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 只是有點吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麽了我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.50,0:10:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.97,0:10:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回學校上課了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.26,0:10:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麽事了嗎 諾諾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還裝模作樣地給你取這種名字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.70,0:10:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿幾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.32,0:10:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.18,0:10:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到老師了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.29,0:10:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.39,0:11:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.12,0:11:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麽事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.86,0:11:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.41,0:11:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說篤史那傢夥在騷擾那女人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.10,0:11:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 有沒有什麽辦法能解決呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你直接去跟篤史說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.37,0:11:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我老爸說了同樣的話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.63,0:11:29.11,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(170,650)\c&H1414FF&}せき
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.63,0:11:29.11,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(590,650)\c&H1414FF&}カカシ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.63,0:11:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1414FF&}隻{\r}之間只有為了{\c&H1414FF&}案山子{\r}的事才能互相起爭執
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:31.91,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(460,650)\c&H1414FF&}カカシ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那沒有{\c&H1414FF&}案山子{\r}的話就什麽也做不了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.65,0:11:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說阿幾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.48,0:11:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得老師怎麽樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...沒什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那以後 關於老師的惡評在村子裡不斷擴大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.61,0:12:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過得還真是辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.88,0:12:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是老想著被挨揍的老好人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.98,0:12:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽樣 放棄掙扎做我的女人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.67,0:12:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只臭狗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.38,0:12:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.02,0:12:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.14,0:12:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.24,0:12:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了你 我得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.41,0:12:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你那樣做真的沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.87,0:13:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是你同父異母的哥哥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麽辦法 是他先動手的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.62,0:13:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麽事情會變成這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來這村子就已經是錯誤了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.90,0:13:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是沒有其它的工作了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.86,0:13:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你和你學生的爸爸幽會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.47,0:13:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 大家都已經知道了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.62,0:13:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會看不起我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.19,0:13:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不會...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.99,0:13:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是只有父子的單親家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.57,0:13:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在照顧他的時候...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.37,0:13:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是太輕率了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今還深深烙印在我腦海中的 是那孩子心碎般的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.37,0:13:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好 那孩子保住了性命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:14:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果因為這件事情 我也辭掉了學校的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.46,0:14:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和他有著相同的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.47,0:14:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和當時那孩子一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.52,0:14:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常之遙遠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷彿什麽都不放進眼裡的空虛眼神...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把我當成那個小鬼來泄憤嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.04,0:14:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真卑鄙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.93,0:14:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壞心眼的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.98,0:14:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我就是要泄憤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.29,0:14:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你一起遠走高飛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.87,0:14:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你兩個人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.77,0:14:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.76,0:14:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡還有要做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:57.04,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(510,650)\c&H1414FF&}クラミツハ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1414FF&}暗密刀{\r}是屬於我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.48,0:15:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情好像變得越發奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.58,0:15:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我陪你玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 還真是無拘無束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.87,0:15:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和那個女人都是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.66,0:15:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 來這邊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.71,0:15:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跑得真快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.01,0:15:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空真高遠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.99,0:15:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的夏天就要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.83,0:15:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.99,0:15:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我對老師...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匡平君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.38,0:15:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匡平君你要一直做阿幾的朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.18,0:16:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是遺憾 瀨能老師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.02,0:16:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在小朋友裡的評價也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.25,0:16:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也對妳有很大的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.18,0:16:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在問題一再地發生 這樣下去的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.65,0:16:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰把這個...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.21,0:16:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是關鍵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.82,0:16:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也有這裡的規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳已經觸犯了這個規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.83,0:16:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上不聽我再三的忠告去接近阿幾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.25,0:16:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳似乎不具備我們所追求的老師該有的良知
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.14,0:16:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.13,0:16:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙您這段時間的照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.28,0:16:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾諾?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾諾 諾諾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真叫人意外呢 阿幾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.97,0:17:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你會為了一個女人而來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.21,0:17:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是還真是可惜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢夥已經不是你專屬的女人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.49,0:17:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賤人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說阿幾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.82,0:17:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的吧 我非常討厭你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.56,0:18:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從把你這二房生的小鬼帶到家裡來時就一直很討厭你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但如此 也不知道出了什麽差錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.68,0:18:13.22,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(660,650)\c&H1414FF&}クラミツハ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.68,0:18:13.22,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(820,650)\c&H1414FF&}せき
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.68,0:18:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本應該是我被選上當{\c&H1414FF&}暗密刀{\r}的{\c&H1414FF&}隻{\r} 現在也被你搶去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.49,0:18:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這玩意回歸到我手裡之前的這幾年間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.56,0:18:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我是什麽心情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得我會明白人渣的心情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.85,0:18:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是服了你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.79,0:18:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死到臨頭 還一副令人憎惡的口吻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.64,0:18:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.42,0:18:35.60,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(770,650)\c&H1414FF&}クラミツハ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.42,0:18:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你最愛的{\c&H1414FF&}暗密刀{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.89,0:18:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.70,0:18:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好開心 你來救我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.30,0:19:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你兩個人一起遠走高飛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.19,0:19:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個傻女人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.78,0:19:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.29,0:19:14.12,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(860,650)\c&H1414FF&}カカシ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.29,0:19:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我的命令啊 笨蛋{\c&H1414FF&}案山子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篤史 不是說只是讓他們吃點苦頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.53,0:19:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒說過要殺人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.73,0:19:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩給我一起殉情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 是殉情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.29,0:19:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 這次我可是來真的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你的恩怨也累積了這麽久
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.08,0:19:39.36,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,650)\c&H11414FF&}クラミツハ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.08,0:19:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1414FF&}暗密刀{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.68,0:19:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能再次回到我身邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.16,0:19:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索性就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.78,0:19:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.68,0:20:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽 怎麽回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.29,0:20:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快幹掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:04.86,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,650)\c&H1414FF&}クラミツハ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1414FF&}暗密刀{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.90,0:20:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.04,0:20:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篤史大人  到底怎麽了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.26,0:20:10.72,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(800,650)\c&H1414FF&}カカシ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.26,0:20:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然都叫出了{\c&H1414FF&}案山子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.95,0:20:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿幾  那女人是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.81,0:20:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這究竟是怎麽回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.45,0:20:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女人是小學的老師吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.71,0:20:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篤史大人 到底發生了什麽事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.58,0:20:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 我什麽都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:24.38,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(800,650)\c&H1414FF&}クラミツハ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是阿幾和{\c&H1414FF&}暗密刀{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.46,0:20:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麽回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿幾到底做了什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:29.48,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(400,650)\c&H1414FF&}クラミツハ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:29.48,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(560,650)\c&H1414FF&}せき
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1414FF&}暗密刀{\r}的{\c&H1414FF&}隻{\r}不是篤史大人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.67,0:20:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.71,0:21:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是匡平嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.73,0:21:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些全部都是你幹的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.00,0:21:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 終於都恢復原狀了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.62,0:21:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.20,0:21:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於又和你在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.86,0:21:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.06,0:21:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.31,0:21:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定要...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.66,0:21:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.21,0:21:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 匡平
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.28,0:21:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿幾!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.62,0:22:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就這麽結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.90,0:22:55.89,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(660,650)\c&H1414FF&}クラミツハ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.90,0:22:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢夥與{\c&H1414FF&}暗密刀{\r}的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.04,0:22:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最後還是依舊成謎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.37,0:23:00.06,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(560,650)\c&H1414FF&}クラミツハ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.37,0:23:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1414FF&}暗密刀{\r}被封印
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.68,0:23:02.27,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(800,650)\c&H1414FF&}せき
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.68,0:23:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我放棄了當{\c&H1414FF&}隻{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.81,0:23:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事後我才知道老師不是他殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.00,0:23:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨看樣子停了

Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.66,0:23:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽次回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.64,0:23:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故事將再次回到都市
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.28,0:23:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神明的職責
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.00,0:23:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定...要...看哦
